org.jerkar.tool

Class JkImportedRuns

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jerkar.tool.JkImportedRuns

  • public final class JkImportedRuns
extends java.lang.Object
    A run class can import one or several run classes. It is an important mechanism to reuse runs across projects. This class holds imported runs within a run class.
